  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the trial is to determine the accuracy of Cu-64 labelled DOTATATE for
      diagnosing cardiac sarcoidosis using PET/CT or PET/MRI.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
